I can see the sign-in page is set up to show Google login if the Google provider is available. The issue is that the Google credentials are not configured in the environment variables. 

Since we don't have Google OAuth credentials set up, I should either:
1. Remove the Google provider from the auth configuration (simplest)
2. Or add a note to set up Google OAuth
